Each day of the NAMM show, they produced a mag that outlined the days events as well as product releases. This mag, which my brought back two copies of for me is the size of a Billboard magazine. My wife was on a conference in L.A. last week and part of what she had to do, was attend the NAMM show in Anaheim. (North America Musical Instrument Manufacturers) trade show. She was clicking maddly at anything and everyone she thought "looked important" LOL So far, we have been able to identify everyone she has taken a pic of, except this group. They had mega median surrounding them, so, of course, my wife thought them to be stars or soon to be stars! She managed to squeeze in through the media horde and snap ths pic below. The guy on the left in the pic, gave her an "atta girl" for her tenacity. Now I probably wouldn't want to run into these guys in a dark alley, but my wife said they were really nice guys and very down to earth... So, can anyone here identify who these guys are?  Also, can anyone identify this dude! LOL  This guy is apparently the producer of Canada's own "Heart". He's also their lead guitar player  Sorry for the non fishing post, but it is winter and I thought this may be a decent diversion from the day to day grind.
